Mental Vacation is a growing series of unique digital sculptures by BASPHI. Each artwork is hand-sculpted in Virtual Reality and comes with multiple files stored on Arweave:

// Image (2000 x 2000px JPG)
// Video (1000 x 1000px MP4)
// 3D/AR files (GLB + REALITY)
// Profile Picture (1000 x 1000px JPG)

View on: [www.mentalvacation.xyz/001](https://mentalvacation.xyz/001)

It also comes with a signed 15x20cm print on heavy paper that will be shipped worldwide via mail. It can get claimed after purchase via dm or email.

